{"tid":1679660,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《有圖》香港人除左用200億養狗咬自己不特止 仲用緊194億去養垃圾","createTime":"2019-10-28T10:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T08:14:46.000Z","uid":32048,"like":107,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"9410d4e11e1fdca8564b0c134ef278c1e912818c","tid":1679660,"uid":32048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:25:48.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係我繼續狙擊社福界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當大家屌緊黑警每年用200億同譴責班國際人道組織一年吸金20億既時候<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1492843/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1492843/page/1</a> ，其實我地香港人今年係用左194億去俾本地既社福機構，無錯，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係194億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyrGxjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrGxjR.jpg&h=3c1893b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢4個月黎青少年既濫捕、被消失，青年機構無講過一句野<br />\n請老人家同小朋友食tg，老人同兒童團體都無講過一句野<br />\n手足被人拉，支援佢地既外展隊不見蹤影<br />\n無飯食同要心理輔導既手足，都見唔到有社福機構出黎幫<br />\n<br />\n收錢奶共，救世軍賣物資賺大錢，性公會救陳同佳，遊協同777玩閉門，社署出信叫中心唔好開門俾手足避，前線義務社工被捕被清算，依一切就係依家既社福界<br />\n<br />\n樓豬搵左文筆好既朋友幫手寫緊查詢(投訴)信，希望下一個po 手足們多多捧場，唔好再俾社福機構袋左錢唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 請保持憤怒 唔可以慣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"8587603dab9a6720fab98fb8a573cdd0c9978079","tid":1679660,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4568fa320bca24fb09c1bea87bb1f1e1b297be94","tid":1679660,"uid":32048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"推<img 