re":0,"quote":{"pid":"9410d4e11e1fdca8564b0c134ef278c1e912818c","tid":1679660,"uid":32048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:25:48.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係我繼續狙擊社福界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當大家屌緊黑警每年用200億同譴責班國際人道組織一年吸金20億既時候<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1492843/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1492843/page/1</a> ，其實我地香港人今年係用左194億去俾本地既社福機構，無錯，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係194億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyrGxjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrGxjR.jpg&h=3c1893b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢4個月黎青少年既濫捕、被消失，青年機構無講過一句野<br />\n請老人家同小朋友食tg，老人同兒童團體都無講過一句野<br />\n手足被人拉，支援佢地既外展隊不見蹤影<br />\n無飯食同要心理輔導既手足，都見唔到有社福機構出黎幫<br />\n<br />\n收錢奶共，救世軍賣物資賺大錢，性公會救陳同佳，遊協同777玩閉門，社署出信叫中心唔好開門俾手足避，前線義務社工被捕被清算，依一切就係依家既社福界<br />\n<br />\n樓豬搵左文筆好既朋友幫手寫緊查詢(投訴)信，希望下一個po 手足們多多捧場，唔好再俾社福機構袋左錢唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 請保持憤怒 唔可以慣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"講!要做咩！全力支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a81c518d9edcdb09a3be9bc1e09a2e1945a663","tid":1679660,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" clas